        <fn id="t002fn001">
          <p>For clarity, only the most meaningful results of the benchmark are shown here. The full results are provided as supporting information and the assembly workflows are also better visualized there (<xref ref-type="supplementary-material" rid="pone.0216885.s003">S1 Table</xref>). The best gap filling results for each of the draft genomes are presented as bold font figures (columns 7 and 8).</p>
